899
01:18:24.559 --> 01:18:26.360
You bastard, Sanjay!

900
01:18:52.000 --> 01:18:52.840
Come here.

901
01:18:55.120 --> 01:18:56.840
I don't want to live like this anymore!

902
01:18:58.480 --> 01:19:01.360
So you just want to have fun here?

903
01:19:02.320 --> 01:19:05.120
