for 20 years,

924
01:21:10.679 --> 01:21:12.160
I should know my place and leave.

925
01:21:14.040 --> 01:21:16.360
My heart is asking to heal.

926
01:21:19.360 --> 01:21:21.440
If my sacrifice meant nothing,

927
01:21:22.360 --> 01:21:25.920
why should I stay
when you still feel helpless?

928
01:21:28.200 --> 01:21:30.240
Your existence makes me sad, Devi.

929
01:21:31.040 --> 01:21:32.480
It breaks my heart.

930
01:21:38.639 --> 01:21:40.480
THE JOURNEY OF THE LEGENDS

931
01:21:40.559 --> 01:21:41.679
You know…

932
01:21:42.920 --> 01:21:44.639
Mumbai is close to Tibet.

933
01:21:45.679 --> 01:21:47.080
Dalai Lama's city.

934
01:22:20.040 --> 01:22:21.200
Your mom

935
