left this letter for you.

936
01:22:30.080 --> 01:22:31.559
Keep it safe, okay?

937
01:22:38.559 --> 01:22:40.160
My dear Amitabh.

938
01:22:41.200 --> 01:22:42.679
My daughter, Devi,

939
01:22:43.519 --> 01:22:45.920
believes that you are her dad.

940
01:22:46.599 --> 01:22:49.360
She loves dancing just like you.

941
01:22:50.719 --> 01:22:52.679
She wants to make you proud.

942
01:22:53.480 --> 01:22:58.200
Even though there's already someone
who admires her and is very proud of her.

943
01:22:59.760 --> 01:23:00.800
If you want to know,

944
01:23:01.320 --> 01:23:03.360
his name is Emir.

945
01:23:04.280 --> 01:23:08.480
Emir obeyed all of Devi's wishes

946
