while I was at the cinema.

953
01:23:34.760 --> 01:23:37.920
Not in bed with my real husband.

954
01:23:39.360 --> 01:23:41.240
Poor Devi's dad.

955
01:23:42.080 --> 01:23:45.440
He left because he felt
you were his rival.

956
01:23:46.120 --> 01:23:49.040
But there's no harm in him
keeping my dreams alive.

957
01:23:49.639 --> 01:23:51.360
It was just a dream.

958
01:23:51.440 --> 01:23:54.080
It could never be real.

959
01:23:56.200 --> 01:23:58.880
There you are, in your sparkling world.

960
01:23:59.760 --> 01:24:02.480
And I'm here, in Kerinci,

961
01:24:02.559 --> 01:24:07.160
a place that only shines
when the stars appear at night.

962
01:24:09.000 --> 01:24:09.960
I am sorry.

963
01:24:10.760 --> 01:24:13.200
I can't come to meet you.

964
01:24:14.200 --> 01:24:15.400
I'm unwell.

965
01:24:16.519 --> 01:24:19.040
Traveling long distances is impossible.

966
01:24:20.440 --> 01:24:23.480
But I send our daughter,

967
01:24:24.080 --> 01:24:27.840
Devi, who brought this letter to you.

968
01:24:28.920 --> 01:24:30.800
And I introduce Emir to you,

969
01:24:31.400 --> 01:24:34.679
the young man who has always been
her protective knight.

970
