back then.

1050
01:30:28.320 --> 01:30:29.240
Yes…

1051
01:30:30.639 --> 01:30:31.559
Yes.

1052
01:30:34.160 --> 01:30:36.080
I don't understand

1053
01:30:37.160 --> 01:30:39.400
how to show

1054
01:30:40.400 --> 01:30:42.160
my love to your mom.

1055
01:30:50.040 --> 01:30:53.400
I don't belong here right now.

1056
01:31:02.679 --> 01:31:03.880
You belong here.

